<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Link Not Found</title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family:Segoe UI;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            background:#e4e8eb;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            background: white;
            padding: 1.8rem 0.7em 0.9em 0.7em;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 90%;
            width: 550px;
        }

        .icon-container {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .icon-circle {
            background: #fee2e2;
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .icon-circle i {
            font-size: 25px;
            color: #dc2626;
        }

        .message {
            font-size: 1.35rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        .info {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #6b7280;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .container {
                padding: 0.9rem;
            }

            .message {
                font-size: 1.3rem;
            }

            .info {
                font-size: 0.8rem;
            }

            .icon-circle {
                width: 60px;
                height: 60px;
            }

            .icon-circle i {
                font-size: 25px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="icon-container">
            <div class="icon-circle">
                <i class="fas fa-link-slash"></i>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="message">Link Not Found !! Try Reloading Page</div>
        <div class="info">
            The link you are trying to access was not found.<br>
            Please contact the link owner for further assistance.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>